<plot>A long time ago there was an evil Captain who was a very greedy person. He heard that there was a beautiful crown which was cursed by a wizard in a kingdom far away. He didn't believe in curses, so he attacked the kingdom and he stole the Crown. But once he put the crown on his head, he turned into a painting. His crew was so afraid they jumped overboard and his ship sank because it was destroyed on the rocks. The crown sank in the sea and the painting floated on the water...</plot><url>http://localhost:8983/solr/movie.html?432461</url></doc>
